This paper discusses the evaluation of topic models, which is a common task in natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR), falling under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of automated metrics, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the analysis of datasets, which is a common task in data science (cs.DS).
